                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.51/5740: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in China (<persName type="from"
                            >Johnson</persName>) to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Peiping</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-02-09T14:00:00+08:00"
                            >February 9, 1933—2 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received February 9—6:20 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>132. My 116, February 4, 11 a.m. I have just learned that National City Bank of
                    New York was offered the loan on a competitive bid basis.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Johnson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
